{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 398.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- to the men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- and the clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to take off the coat and put it on a mountain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mountains, already, of clothes were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A German, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Nazi with-- with-- with the-- with the-- and we walked out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then told us to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, there were so many feet deep, honest to God, on the street, you know, with people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was staying down there with-- with a little girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She went to school together from our street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Areva ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Smaller. ?] Her brother, two brothers, still live there in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said to me, she turns around to her mother, and she says, mom, I don't-- I can't see you being dead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said to me, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I turned around to her, I said, can't neither.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, let's stay in front of our mothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when they kill, maybe they'll kill us first, or if they kill them, we won't see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know where they're taking us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Someplace to kill or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know they're going to kill us, but you know-- by that time, they came and took us away again over the road, two streets further on a marketplace.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came to that marketplace I said to-- I was staying with-- with my mother, you know, and I was so hugging her.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A German came over to me and he said, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was going to say 14, and she's-- my mother pushed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's 16.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In what language did he ask you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in German, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, she's 16, and she pushed me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as she pushed me, I pushed myself back.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
